translations: 无可指责的；无可怀疑的；无懈可击的；无过失的，无罪的

sentences.sentence: He said all five were men of unimpeachable character.
sentences.translation: 他说五个男人都有诚实可靠的性格。

sentences.sentence: They finally got evidence from an unimpeachable source.
sentences.translation: 他们最后得到了来源可靠的证据。

sentences.sentence: Solomon Gills is in the act of seeing what time it is by the unimpeachable chronometer.
sentences.translation: 所罗门·吉尔斯那时正在看他那只完美无缺的精密计时表，看看是什么时候了。
